[%csl Ra5]}) 19. axb4 axb4 20. Rfc1 Qd6 21. Rc4 $14 {[%csl Rb4] white has a
clear target, while black is on the defensive.}) {However, white has a strong
reply:} 11. Ng5 $1 {[%cal Ge3e4] reinforcing the threat e3-e4.} h6 (11... c5 $6
{only helps white} 12. e4 $1 cxd4 13. exf5 dxc3 14. fxg6 hxg6 15. Qxc3 Ra7 16.
