then the knight} f6 {white can calmly retreat} 15. Nd3 $1 {[%csl Rb4,Rc5][%cal
Gd3b4,Gd3c5]} Bf7 {and start attacking black's new weaknesses with} 16. a3 {
[%csl Rb4]}) 13. Nxg6 hxg6 {Black survived the worst as he swapped his
vulnerable light-squared bishop. White is nevertheless better due to many
