advantage with} 9. cxb5 $1 cxb5 10. g4 Be6 11. Bg2 {[%csl Ra8][%cal Gg2a8]
cxb5 was needed to open up the long diagonal.} Bd5 12. f3 $1 {[%csl Ge4][%cal
