Bxf3 e6 (13... f6 $5 14. Nd3 e5 15. e4 Bb7 16. d5 $14) 14. O-O Ra7 15. e4 Ba8
16. Be3 $36 {[%csl Ra7,Gd4,Ge4,Ge5][%cal Gf1f7] with obvious advantage for
