(2590)-Vo,T (2318)/Ho Chi Minh City 2013/CBM 153 Extra (43)}) (7... b4 $6 8.
Na4 Nfd7 {1-0 Hawkins,J (2503)-Fernandez,D (2352)/Blackpool 2013/CBM 153 Extra
