} h5 23. Nd4 $1 $14 {[%csl Gc7,Gd4,Ge5][%cal Gd4c6,Gc6a7] when the pawn on c7
and active pieces more than compensate for the missing exchange.}) 16. Nxb5 $1
{Strong and undoubtedly prepared by Wojtaszek before the game.} axb5 17. Bxb5 {
[%csl Rc6,Re8][%cal Gb5e8] The pin is very unpleasant for black.} Rc8 ({The
