Rd1 $1 {[%csl Re7][%cal Gd1d7]} Nb6 {Here Wojtaszek went for the material with}
22. Ba3+ ({Although} 22. a4 $1 $146 {[%csl Re7][%cal Ga4a5]} Nd5 23. Rd4 {
[%cal Ge3e4] seems to be even more decisive.}) 22... Kf6 23. Rd8 Bxa3 24. Rxh8
$16 {which he tried to convert for another 130-odd moves, but ultimately black
